| comment "Dragnet [Ransomware]: dragnet-ransomware-2024-0645 — Recovery Inhibition (arcusmedia)"
| comment "Status: experimental | Level: high | ID: 2e5a0698-5ce4-5f0a-bf94-fa3e79efa24e"
